== Ubuzima bwa Willy muri make ==
Willy Ndahiro yavukiye mu [[Burundi]] muri 1976, muri 1993 we n'umuryango we batashye mu [[Rwanda]]. muri 1993 Willy yahise ajya mu gisirikare aho yabaye mu ngabo zirinda perezida kugeza 2006.<ref>Acting was my childhood dream– Ndahiro | The New Times | Rwanda</ref><ref>Rwandan filmmakers challenged to form associations <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › section › read</ref> Willy avuye mu gisirikare yasubiye kwiga arangiriza mu bumenyi bw'ikoranabuhanga, muri 2006 nibwo yatangiye inzira yo gukina filimi atangirira kuri filimi yahise ituma amenyekana "Ikigeragezo cy'ubuzima"<ref>Umukinnyi wa filime Willy Ndahiro yagaragaje ibishyira hasi sinema nyarwanda - Kigali Today</ref>, muri 2010 yayoboye ndetse akina muyindi filimi yakunzwe cyane "Ay'urukundo"<ref>Movie industry needs more money - The East African</ref>. Willy kandi yagiye ashinga studio zitunganya amafilimi harimo iyakoze filmi nyinshi yitwa"Vision Production Ltd"<ref>Filmmaker Ndahiro unveils new film production studio <nowiki>https://www.newtimes.co.rw</nowiki> › entertainment › filmmak...</ref>
